title: Wrong summoner level on profile
body: I'm a level 30 and it says i'm a level 5, not sure why. Please help and thank you for your time.

replies.body: When posting for the first time, your account may need to sync with the boards.  It looks like your post here has made that update.  Let me know if you have any issues posting now!

Hey Porocles, not to hyjack this guy's thread, but why doesn't my season2 gold show on the boards? it's not a big enough issue to make a thread about, but it's weird!

http://prntscr.com/djfput

I'm not really sure, it may be some syncing issue or something with the boards that I don't really have visibility on.  I tried to look into this to adjust it for you, but had no luck.  You may want to post about forum icons on the[ boards feedback ](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/site-feedback)section to report this.  Good luck!
